 Fast-rising Nigerian Skit Maker, Mandy Kiss has finally come out to speak on the allegation going around about her being the side chick of colleague, Cute Abiola. The gossip which was first brought to light by controversial Instagram blogger, Gistlover, who accused comedian, Abdulgafar Abiola popularly known as Cute Abiola of having multiple lovers one amongst many is Mandy Kiss. Reacting to the news Mandy Kiss, in a video that surfaced online, lashes at those sliding into her DM and asking to know the truth about the allegation. Mandy Kiss said people could choose to believe whatever they read online because she owes nobody any explanation regarding the news making rounds online. The upcoming actress added that she owes her body, and even if she had sex with Cute Abiola or not, it is nobody’s business. Watch video below; 